    <div class="game-section">
      <h3>How Nines works</h3>
      <p>Nines is a three-player points game. Each hole distributes exactly 9 points across the three players based on net score finish order. Lowest net score takes the most points; highest net score takes the least.</p>
      <p>The clever part: when players tie, the tied points are split evenly. This ensures every hole always totals 9 points regardless of ties.</p>

